parameters: Pony-Celes: "Found it. This must be the original!"
01_怪人サイミンダーグ_デフォルト
Chairman: "How dare you do that to the original!!"

Pony-Celes: "That form... It seems you can't transform into a
monster without the original operating!"

Pony-Celes: "You have no chance of winning now. Prepare yourself,
Chairman!"

Chairman: "They are the elite Zyborgs, directly under Lord Domdora's
command!"

parameters.name: ポニーセレスのテーマ

parameters: Principal: "Such... a warrior directly under Lord Domudra!"
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘むすっとB

Pony-Celes: "Domudra... that coward who would even betray his own
comrades."
Principal: "A coward, you say! How rude!"

Principal: "Lord Domudra picked me up... and praised my hypnotism
skills! A noble person indeed!"

Principal: "He saw potential in my talent, and made me the principal
of this academy!"
Principal: "Lord Domudra is my justice! His orders are absolute!!"
01_ポニーセレス_戦闘冷たい目
Pony-Celes: "Zyda-G is a group of evil that disturbs the peace!"
Pony-Celes: "No matter the reason, what you're doing is wrong!"

Pony-Celes: "Now, tell me where he is. I'll go and give him a lesson
myself!"
Principal: "...Understood. You're right. I'll tell you where he is."
Principal: "Who would say such a thing!!"

Principal: "It seems like a mistake not to have taken away your
freedom to move your legs! Ha-ha-ha-ha!"

Pony-Celes: "Next time we meet, it won't be so easy for you, be
prepared!"
Chairman: "Oh! Well done! You did great!"
Chairman: "After all the unnecessary things you've done..."
Chairman: "This level of damage is no problem!"
Chairman: "Come on, get up. You need to wake up!"
Chairman: "Now, let's have you reveal your true identity."
Chairman: "You seem to know a lot about this academy, who are you?"
Pony-Celes: "Who would... Who would say that!"

Chairman: "You still don't understand the situation you're in, do
you?"
Chairman: "Now, let's hear your true identity."
Chairman: "I can't believe Pony-Celes' true identity was Morisaki..."

Chairman: "Are you the only fool who dares to oppose Zyda? Isn't
there an accomplice among the students?"
Chairman: "As I thought... You were closest to him after all."
Chairman: "What! You two are in that kind of relationship?!"

Chairman: "Damn you, Amasawa! To think you'd lay your hands on my
favorite Morisaki... Unforgivable!"
Chairman: "Heh heh heh, I've got a good idea."

Chairman: "He'll get a good look at Morisaki and me loving each other,
up close and personal!"

Chairman: "I can't wait to see the look on Amasawa's face. Heh heh
heh!"
\c[27]From this point on, a tragic end awaits Pony-Celes.
